text: "Spaceman" is a 1972 song by Harry Nilsson and taken from his seventh studio album Son of Schmilsson. It went to number 12 in Canada, number 23 in the United States and number 95 in Australia. It was used in the HBO television series Avenue 5. == References == Category:1972 songs Category:Harry Nilsson songs Category:Pop rock songs
